rules.description: Razer Naga Pro 1 to Cmd + T
Razer Naga Pro 3 to Cmd + W
Razer Naga Pro 6 to Fast forward
Keyboard Ins to Alfred Dark Mode

to_if_held_down.shell_command: osascript -e 'tell application id "com.runningwithcrayons.Alfred" to run trigger "com.punydev.dm" in workflow "com.shayon.wrkflw.darkMode"'

rules.description: Keyboard Pg Up to Volume Up
Keyboard Pg Down to Volume Down
Keyboard Command + PgUp to Pg Up
Keyboard Hyper Key + Pg Up to Display Brightness Up
Keyboard Hyper Key + Spacebar to show spotlight
Keyboard Hyper Key + PgDown to Display Brightness Down
Keyboard Hyper Key + Right to Next Track
Keyboard Hyper Key + Left to Previous Track
Keyboard Hyper Key + Enter to Play/Pause

to.shell_command: osascript -e 'tell application "Keyboard Maestro Engine" to do script "41F1AD11-77BA-414C-97FB-F0F4C1F7600C"'
